Package it.danja.newsmonitor.model

Interface DateStamp

All Known Implementing Classes:
DateStampImpl
public interface DateStamp
Encapsulates dates associated with @FeedEntity stored as ISO8601 strings published and upStringd are derived from feed content (if available) seen is generated when the feed is read
